    <item>
      <title>Latex Test</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/latex-test/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 13:24:40 +0100</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/latex-test/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;lorem-ipsum&#34;&gt;Lorem Ipsum&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, &lt;em&gt;consectetur&lt;/em&gt; adipiscing elit. &lt;strong&gt;Integer nec odio.&lt;/strong&gt; Praesent libero. Sed cursus ante dapibus diam. Sed nisi. Nulla quis sem at nibh elementum imperdiet.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;equations&#34;&gt;Equations&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Here is an example of a LaTeX-style equation:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$$
E = mc^2
$$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;theorems--proofs&#34;&gt;Theorems &amp;amp; Proofs&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;::: theorem
This is a sample theorem.
:::&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;::: lemma
This is a sample lemma.
:::&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;::: proof
Here is a proof for the theorem.
:::&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;lists&#34;&gt;Lists&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Item 1&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Item 2&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Item 3&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;table&#34;&gt;Table&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
  &lt;thead&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;th&gt;Column 1&lt;/th&gt;
          &lt;th&gt;Column 2&lt;/th&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
  &lt;/thead&gt;
  &lt;tbody&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;A&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;B&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;C&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;D&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
  &lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;footnotes&#34;&gt;Footnotes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an example of a footnote&lt;sup id=&#34;fnref:1&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#fn:1&#34; class=&#34;footnote-ref&#34; role=&#34;doc-noteref&#34;&gt;1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;footnotes&#34; role=&#34;doc-endnotes&#34;&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li id=&#34;fn:1&#34;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is the footnote text.&amp;#160;&lt;a href=&#34;#fnref:1&#34; class=&#34;footnote-backref&#34; role=&#34;doc-backlink&#34;&gt;&amp;#x21a9;&amp;#xfe0e;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
</description>
    </item>
    
    
    
    <item>
      <title>Welcome</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/welcome/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 12:44:11 +0100</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/welcome/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;markdown-latexcss-test&#34;&gt;Markdown LaTeX.css Test&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;theorems--definitions&#34;&gt;Theorems &amp;amp; Definitions&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;theorem&#34;&gt;Theorem&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;theorem&#34;&gt;
This is an example of a theorem. It should be styled with a left border and italicized text.
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;lemma&#34;&gt;Lemma&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;lemma&#34;&gt;
This is an example of a lemma. It should look similar to a theorem but be labeled as a Lemma.
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;definition&#34;&gt;Definition&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;definition&#34;&gt;
A &lt;strong&gt;definition&lt;/strong&gt; should be clearly distinguishable from theorems and lemmas. It provides formal explanations.
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;proof&#34;&gt;Proof&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;proof&#34;&gt;
We begin with the given assumptions and apply known results. Finally, we arrive at the conclusion.
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;proof-with-ending-symbol&#34;&gt;Proof with Ending Symbol&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;proof&#34;&gt;
This proof should have a right-aligned ending symbol.
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;lists-and-blockquotes&#34;&gt;Lists and Blockquotes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;ordered-list&#34;&gt;Ordered List&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;First item&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Second item&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Third item&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;unordered-list&#34;&gt;Unordered List&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bullet point one&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bullet point two&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bullet point three&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;blockquote&#34;&gt;Blockquote&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a blockquote. It should have a left border and an italicized font.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;code-blocks&#34;&gt;Code Blocks&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-python&#34; data-lang=&#34;python&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;# Python example&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nf&#34;&gt;theorem_proof&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;x&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;):&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;    &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;x&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;**&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;x&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
    </item>
    
    
